ngue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過其實ground可能玩得仲癲<br />\n做crew都話可能日日拍唔同人<br />\n隨時大家係同事但你都唔識佢係邊個<br />\n食唔食得都唔知<br />\n<br />\n相反ground工作時間長<br />\n分分鐘對住同事仲多過對屋企人男女朋友<br />\n仲要日日都係見住嗰班人<br />\n然後啲更又亂過閪<br />\n隨時你嘅另一半都唔知你幾時返工幾時收工幾時放假(因為可能你自己都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n所以大把airport only 嘅關係<br />\n加上機場啲殘廁又大又乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c093324762f725da7012e484e6f8998084926bdf","tid":863341,"uid":64481,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bfe97c9fb6eb66bb052db2ac112864d245f4c5bb","tid":863341,"uid":137694,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T15:28:44.000Z","msg":"空少真係特别多gay"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T20:13:26.000Z","msg":"又真係好多都好gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4659ba7f3466b194d8e6485deab4a31c2bd6d442","tid":863341,"uid":44580,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T20:29:18.000Z","msg":"佢都係唔想你煩住佢佢先耕揾個故仔呃你<br />\n佢呃完你 自己又可以含洋腸 幾好啊"},{"pid":"2cf5b9080b727e24401c2c4f060feb288799e812","tid":863341,"uid":158806,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T20:58:34.000Z","msg":"空少真係特别多gay<br />\n<br />\n我個空姐朋友都係咁講"},{"pid":"d2724864794cb2650f7ceb3c501eaba61767f098","tid":863341,"uid":155732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5210a8a40e3fbafc7a925a48ef8a2c8b53cd445a","tid":863341,"uid":123335,"like":35,"dislike":206,"score":-171,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T13:49:24.000Z","msg":"初初我都以為我朋友條女一做空姐會好淫亂 <br />\n本身以為飛得 散得 <br />\n點知原來呢行根本唔淫 <br />\n之前真係怪錯左佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T21:10:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif